  "text": "Wide-spectrum filters can be applied to ac drives with diode or silicon-controlled rectifier precharge input rectifiers and can be applied to single or multiple drives. The filter can be usually retrofitted to existing drives without the requirement for drive modifications, whether for single-or for multiple-drive applications. This method has been described in [CITATION_1] .",
